<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Crime Reporting Portal</title>
    <style>
        *{margin:0;padding:0;box-sizing:border-box;}

        body{
            font-family:'Segoe UI',sans-serif;
            background:linear-gradient(135deg,#1e3c72,#2a5298,#0f2027);
            color:#fff;
            min-height:100vh;
        }

        .header{
            text-align:center;
            padding:20px 10px 15px;
        }

        .logos{
            display:flex;
            justify-content:center;
            gap:20px;
            flex-wrap:wrap;
            margin-bottom:8px;
        }

        .logos img{
            height:110px;
        }

        .title{
            font-size:2rem;
            margin-top:8px;
        }

        .subtitle{
            font-size:1rem;
            opacity:0.9;
            margin-top:4px;
        }

        .container{
            max-width:1200px;
            margin:20px auto 30px;
            padding:0 16px;
            display:grid;
            grid-template-columns:repeat(auto-fit,minmax(260px,1fr));
            gap:24px;
        }

        .card{
            background:rgba(255,255,255,0.08);
            border-radius:18px;
            padding:24px 20px;
            box-shadow:0 8px 25px rgba(0,0,0,0.35);
            backdrop-filter:blur(12px);
            transition:transform .3s ease,box-shadow .3s ease,background .3s ease;
            
            /* KEY: make card a column flexbox */
            display:flex;
            flex-direction:column;
        }

        .card:hover{
            transform:translateY(-8px);
            box-shadow:0 16px 35px rgba(0,0,0,0.45);
            background:rgba(255,255,255,0.16);
        }

        .card img{
            width:80px;
            height:80px;
            border-radius:50%;
            object-fit:cover;
            margin:0 auto 16px;
            border:3px solid rgba(226,103,21,0.6);
        }

        .card h3{
            font-size:1.15rem;
            margin-bottom:10px;
            text-align:center;
        }

        .card p{
            font-size:0.9rem;
            opacity:0.9;
            text-align:center;
        }

        /* button container inside card */
        .card-actions{
            margin-top:auto;           /* pushes this block to bottom */
            display:flex;
            justify-content:center;
            margin-top:18px;
        }

        .btn-register{
            position:relative;
            padding:10px 24px;
            border-radius:999px;
            border:none;
            outline:none;
            cursor:pointer;
            background:linear-gradient(45deg,#e26715,#f4a261);
            color:#fff;
            font-weight:600;
            font-size:0.85rem;
            text-transform:uppercase;
            letter-spacing:0.5px;
            overflow:hidden;
            box-shadow:0 4px 15px rgba(226,103,21,0.5);
            transition:transform .15s ease,box-shadow .15s ease;
            white-space:nowrap;
        }

        .btn-register::after{
            content:"";
            position:absolute;
            width:0;
            height:0;
            top:50%;
            left:50%;
            background:rgba(255,255,255,.4);
            border-radius:50%;
            transform:translate(-50%,-50%);
            transition:width .35s ease,height .35s ease,opacity .4s ease;
            opacity:0;
        }

        .btn-register:hover{
            transform:translateY(-2px);
            box-shadow:0 8px 20px rgba(226,103,21,0.7);
        }

        .btn-register:active{
            transform:translateY(1px) scale(.97);
            box-shadow:0 2px 8px rgba(0,0,0,0.6);
        }

        .btn-register.clicked::after{
            width:260px;
            height:260px;
            opacity:0;
        }

        footer{
            text-align:center;
            padding:18px 10px 24px;
            font-size:.85rem;
            opacity:0.8;
        }

        @media(max-width:600px){
            .title{font-size:1.6rem;}
            .logos img{height:90px;}
            .card{padding:20px 16px;}
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
<header class="header">
    <div class="logos">
        <img src="images/government_of_india.jpg" alt="Government of India">
        <img src="images/mh_police.jpg" alt="Maharashtra Police">
    </div>
    <h1 class="title">Crime Reporting Portal</h1>
    <p class="subtitle">Report incidents securely | सुरक्षित आणि जलद तक्रार नोंदवा</p>
</header>

<div class="container">
    <div class="card">
        <img src="images/E_complaint.jpg" alt="E-Complaint">
        <h3>Online Complaint / ई-तक्रार</h3>
        <p>Register any non-emergency crime online with full details.</p>
        <div class="card-actions">
            <button class="btn-register" data-target="/E_complaint">Register / नोंदणी करा</button>
        </div>
    </div>

    <div class="card">
        <img src="images/missing_person.png" alt="Missing Person">
        <h3>Missing Person / बेपत्ता व्यक्ती</h3>
        <p>Report a missing person with description and last seen details.</p>
        <div class="card-actions">
            <button class="btn-register" data-target="/Missing_person">Register / नोंदणी करा</button>
        </div>
    </div>

    <div class="card">
        <img src="images/undefinedd.jpg" alt="Unidentified Body">
        <h3>Unidentified Dead Body / अज्ञात मृतदेह</h3>
        <p>Provide information about an unidentified body found at any location.</p>
        <div class="card-actions">
            <button class="btn-register" data-target="/Unidentified_body">Register / नोंदणी करा</button>
        </div>
    </div>

    <div class="card">
        <img src="images/cyber crime.avif" alt="Cyber Crime">
        <h3>Cyber Crime / सायबर गुन्हे</h3>
        <p>Report online fraud, harassment, or other cyber offences.</p>
        <div class="card-actions">
            <button class="btn-register" data-target="/Cyber_Crime">Register / नोंदणी करा</button>
        </div>
    </div>

    <div class="card">
        <img src="images/accident.avif" alt="Accident">
        <h3>Accident Case / अपघात प्रकरण</h3>
        <p>Submit accident details including vehicles, injuries, and witnesses.</p>
        <div class="card-actions">
            <button class="btn-register" data-target="/Accident">Register / नोंदणी करा</button>
        </div>
    </div>

    <div class="card">
        <img src="images/lost.png" alt="Lost Items">
        <h3>Missing Items / गहाळ वस्तू</h3>
        <p>File a report for lost documents, valuables, or other items.</p>
        <div class="card-actions">
            <button class="btn-register" data-target="/Missing_Item_forms">Register / नोंदणी करा</button>
        </div>
    </div>
</div>

<footer>
    <p>&copy; 2026 Maharashtra Police. All rights reserved.</p>
</footer>

<script>
    // click ripple + navigation
    document.querySelectorAll('.btn-register').forEach(btn=>{
        btn.addEventListener('click', e=>{
            e.preventDefault();
            btn.classList.remove('clicked');
            void btn.offsetWidth;
            btn.classList.add('clicked');

            const url = btn.dataset.target;
            setTimeout(()=>{ window.location.href = url; }, 200);
        });
    });
</script>
</body>
</html>
